header.gameNote: PROGRESSIVE LEGENDS CLASSIC AT NACOGDOCHES TX

article.headline: Sam Houston St. 65, UC Irvine 63
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Texas -- Darius Gatson scored three of his 13 points in overtime -- a go-ahead layup with 13 seconds remaining and free throw with four seconds left -- as Sam Houston State defeated UC Irvine 65-63 in a Legends Classic game on Wednesday night. DeMarcus Gatlin had 15 points for the Bearkats (3-3). After his overtime basket, Gatson earned a trip to the line by taking a charge against UC Irvine's Alex Young. Adam Folker had 13 points and Will Davis II 12 points and 11 rebounds for the Anteaters (3-3). Folker's layup with 36 seconds remaining in regulation tied the game at 58-all and forced overtime. Terrance Motley had nine points, eight rebounds and three steals off the bench for Sam Houston State.
